{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 75943, "create_time": 1650023524, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "确实踩雷概率大", "timestamp": 1650023524}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 75948, "create_time": 1650023666, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "国外白人导师，从来不安排任何杂活，也不push学生。他最大爱好是写论文带学生。我都有点无聊了，想到我实验室的博士学长还在哼哧哼哧给导师打杂跑腿，真的为自己有机会安安静静深入思考paper idea感到幸运。", "timestamp": 1650023666}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 75970, "create_time": 1650024907, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "我老板算是系里面风评最好的老师之一了，也避免不了干杂活，国内大环境就是这样吧", "timestamp": 1650024907}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 76003, "create_time": 1650027517, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Bob: 老师也要考核的，有时候你不这么干，竞争不过别人", "timestamp": 1650027517}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 76105, "create_time": 1650030358, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "羡慕dz，去的phd学校很一般也比土博好吗？", "timestamp": 1650030358}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 76363, "create_time": 1650064112, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "羡慕了，我天天给导师dz", "timestamp": 1650064112}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 76364, "create_time": 1650064121, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "打杂", "timestamp": 1650064121}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 77004, "create_time": 1650113669, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Dave: 是，PhD主要看导师而非学校", "timestamp": 1650113669}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 77011, "create_time": 1650114153, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "#23397\n所以一定需要多方面、详细了解了导师的为人和实验室情况，才能选择直博。否则，或因时间原因急着做决定，建议无脑选择硕士或申请出国。", "timestamp": 1650114153}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 78982, "create_time": 1650299561, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re 洞主: 真不错啊，怎么查国外老师好不好呢？", "timestamp": 1650299561}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 79424, "create_time": 1650357927, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "Re Grace: 如果能联系到他实验室毕业的学生最好；如果不行，多问问本专业在国外读博的学长学姐，同一个圈子里的多少有些了解；或者去留学论坛上讨论询问\n搬运导师评价洞：#24728", "timestamp": 1650357927}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 110935, "create_time": 1652324773, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "Re : 自然科学领域貌似不存在这个问题，除了杰青你还可以查h-index和被引，还有是否是美国科学会会视，有没有一些奖等等等等，反正自然科学选国内导师很好选", "timestamp": 1652324773}], "create_time": 1650023431, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1652324773, "likenum": 21, "n_attentions": 21, "n_comments": 12, "pid": 27919, "poll": null, "reply": 12, "text": "#27808\n\n和北航北邮的博士同学吃饭，他们告诉我，导师经常让他们干杂活。帮拿快递是最简单的杂活。学生还需要做财务报销、设备建账、仪器购买调试、维修老师家里电器、帮老师写本子写ppt不会得到任何奖金，论文自己工作最后被踢出作者列表、被老师PUA说写的论文是垃圾但又想他读博后、组会全安排在周末、实验室严格打卡考勤扣工资、学术无法提供有效指导、改论文能力极差。。。\n\n于是我润出国了，傍了大佬大腿。中国学术圈不是没有好老师，而是奇葩太多，你遇到好老师概率太少。\n\n因为你真不知道你套磁的杰青优青是真的有科研实力，还是他爸是基金委主任。", "timestamp": 1650023431}}